Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}早已經決定
