Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按開演時間來看 來得是不是太早了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了買演唱會商品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束之後再買不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常來說熱門商品到時候就會賣光的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 你也是個蠻狂熱的歌迷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 昨天怎麼不跟莎拉見見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是對T恤衫和鋼筆那類東西感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要那個手機的高機能外殼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內藏電池 還附帶高音質線性PCM錄音機哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 那還真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想買嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是買的話我倆就湊成一對了 你不介意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請你千萬別買
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的還真乾脆啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點受打擊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長的隊伍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能老老實實排了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還傻站著幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我又不買啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不買也要跟著來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人排隊連聊天對象都沒有會很無聊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來這傢夥 原本不是討厭我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又邀請我來演唱會..又叫我一起排隊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼關係又變好了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望還沒賣光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得這隊伍真的好長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 畢竟是世界性的人氣樂隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來這種大神才不會在這類小場子辦演出啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥 很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機殼GET！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 這背面的LOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND這幾個字的造型美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我覺得很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:07.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~太溜了~好帥~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底還是很狂熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼前被漆成一片碧綠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從未被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我玩捉迷藏的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:46.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lying before me scene painted in green
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was never found 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:58.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when I played hide & seek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉上留下一道小小的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你低頭跪地 苦苦支撐 好似身受重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:04.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there remains a little scar on your face still facing down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:12.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the ground you hold yourself and crouch like you've been wounded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懷念我們無憂無慮胡思亂想的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懷念你靜靜靠在我身邊的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:19.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I adored the days when we just thought the thing with no means oh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:26.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I adored when you were always just there for by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可思議的感覺是怎麼回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我們要在可愛的日本來一首全球首次公開的歌曲
