Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一指示前請待在原處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重復一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.18,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D區域已經被封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.26,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一指示前請待在原處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有非常不好的預感..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開門啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未她怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹的能力被強行激發出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是“崩壞”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D區域之所以被封鎖 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為她的能力讓設施處於半毀狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事 但是由於她的能力太過危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經被拘禁起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥一樣麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這意味著她會在解剖後被處分掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還傻站著幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用你真正的能力就能救她了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為“掠奪”的最強能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 現在時間不多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下我也要被處分掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是心靈感應能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去除雜念..去除雜念..去除雜念..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子裡出現聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是心靈感應能力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到臉的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉..怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 沒你什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..沒必要消除這個人的記憶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我出去 讓我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B區域封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重復一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D區域發生緊急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:14.83,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有職員請按規定就位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到底發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我..救救我..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:21.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.13,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 讓我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以 請告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音..連方向都能確定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你聽得見我的聲音嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有宇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇？你吸收了那種能力麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現的話就糟糕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的狀況已經管不了那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未要被解剖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她擁有了足以破壞設施的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連步未都..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把哥哥救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你穿越時空 改變這個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼過來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 只要眼睛能接觸到光的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七野？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼要為了你這種妹控..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快奪走我的穿透能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說沒時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走這邊 快點去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 不過哥哥他會幫我們改變世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能力怎麼回事..好累人..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了七野的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就來 哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了啊 有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我必須馬上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 之後就拜託你了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 為了未來..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是為了大家..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處分！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在演唱會中昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎..步未她已經..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做惡夢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看到的真的是夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:18:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 之前步未也說過 她覺得我們還有另一位家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好還是再躺一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定有個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..應該有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你想起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊能力發現能力者..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說更明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾了之後倒是蠻帥的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢裡你也出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣貌你應該是第一次見到才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也認識我哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦..是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把一切告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先冷靜 我正是為此而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜跟我來的話 你的所有疑問就會引刃而解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你要去救她 救你的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才..說什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去拯救你的妹妹 乙坂有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的人要怎麼救？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你 應該知道你哥哥隼翼的能力了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你說的隼翼先生 是指那個隼翼先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個人的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我也能去見他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為好久沒見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥變成廢人之後 是他為我指明了前進方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了唯一能夠相信的人 直到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始要步行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我們最不缺的就是錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單而言 就是特殊能力的研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們對我們來說不是敵人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 別囉嗦跟著來就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 我可以拍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是最後的堡壘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥..就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇嗎 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶他們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是..哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒想起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 前泊消除的記憶他並沒有想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除的記憶？那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽這聲音是奈緒醬嗎？好久不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在按照你所指明的道路前進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你幫了我不少忙 你幹的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有宇你呢？我可是你的大哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是感動的再會啊 不過來好好抱抱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在..有些混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子都是問號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真叫人寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可話說回來 這也是自作自受麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼全都說給你聽吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？噗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始講述我那漫長的時空穿越的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要..開始講述什麼呢？
